'''檸檬塔'''（英文：Lemon tart，法文：Tarte au citron）或稱'''檸檬餡餅'''、'''法式檸檬塔'''、'''法式檸檬派'''，是一道由[[麵粉|麵粉]]、[[鮮奶油|奶油]]與[[檸檬|檸檬]]製成的西方甜食點心。

法國的传统做法是把檸檬的卡仕達醬放入派皮後再一起烤<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://frenchmoments.eu/lemon-tart-tarte-au-citron/|title=Lemon Tart - Tarte au citron - French Moments|accessdate=2016-09-29|date=2013-02-18|language=en|archive-date=2021-01-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210103185044/https://frenchmoments.eu/lemon-tart-tarte-au-citron/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，烤完後的派皮口感較濕潤，內餡和派皮的味道能更加完美的融合為一。

改良後的版本是採用預烤法，先把派皮單獨烤過，同時把餡料隔水加熱，烤完和熱完之後就把兩者裝填，再一起烤一段時間就能完成。此種派皮為了節省時間，可以使用[[冰淇淋|冰淇淋]]混合餅乾碎屑，如此就能全面保持塔皮的酥脆口感並增加牛奶的香味；<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://cooking23s.blogspot.tw/2016/08/lemontart.html|title=檸檬塔食譜 : 簡便又能長保酥脆的做法|accessdate=2016-09-29|work=cooking23s.blogspot.tw|archive-date=2017-12-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171201040457/https://cooking23s.blogspot.tw/2016/08/lemontart.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>在

在英國，檸檬餡餅含有烤檸檬奶油的糕點包裝。通常食譜在進行烘烤前加入製作好的[[餡料|餡料]]，有時在上桌前灑上[[糖粉|糖粉]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.raymondblanc.com/recipes/lemon-tart/|title=Lemon Tart|accessdate=2015-01-04|publisher=|archive-date=2021-01-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210124192203/https://www.raymondblanc.com/recipes/lemon-tart/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/tarte_au_citron_94480|title=BBC - Food - Recipes : Tarte au citron|accessdate=2015-01-04|publisher=|archive-date=2021-03-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210306205054/https://www.bbc.co.uk/food/recipes/tarte_au_citron_94480|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.deliaonline.com/recipes/type-of-dish/desserts/tart/deep-lemon-tart.html |title=存档副本 |access-date=2017-05-30 |archive-date=2013-10-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131002055117/http://www.deliaonline.com/recipes/type-of-dish/desserts/tart/deep-lemon-tart.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.maryberry.co.uk/recipes/great-british-bake-off-recipes/classic-lemon-tart|title=Mary Berry|accessdate=2015-01-04|publisher=|archive-date=2019-02-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190226224136/http://www.maryberry.co.uk/recipes/great-british-bake-off-recipes/classic-lemon-tart|dead-url=no}}</ref>；另外餡料也可以在平底鍋中煮熟，然後再加入烤熟的糕點皮中<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.waitrose.com/content/waitrose/en/home/recipes/recipe_directory/h/heston_s_lemon_tart.html|title=Heston's Lemon tart|accessdate=2015-01-04|author=Waitrose Limited|publisher=|archive-date=2021-01-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210123183311/https://www.waitrose.com/content/waitrose/en/home/recipes/recipe_directory/h/heston_s_lemon_tart.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

